### Get Users 
GET {{baseUrl}}/users 
Accept: application/json

### Get User By ID
#Reemplaza el ID con uno válido de tu base de datos para probar la consulta
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/94c298e4-33fe-4a44-99b9-1b4c3ec70a88
Accept: application/json

### Create User
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@northpay.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "operator",
  "firstname": "Test",
  "lastname": "User",
  "phone": "1122334455"
}

### Update User (PATCH)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/00491eb0-9cd7-4d72-bea2-a91b4667ced5
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "Tester",
  "phone": "1199998888"
}

### Soft Delete User
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/00491eb0-9cd7-4d72-bea2-a91b4667ced5
Accept: application/json